{"tid":1386501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！上環示威45人被控暴動罪","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:06:09.000Z","uid":125349,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"54ca8edeb4adec9a5a9d2b31504a616be80579f8","tid":1386501,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">728上環示威45人被控暴動罪</span></span>"},{"pid":"8caf53a2fc8d2939beea89aa51bda5666430a8e7","tid":1386501,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》爭議未平息，上周日(28日)晚上環一帶又發生嚴重警民衝突，警方至今共拘捕49人，他們被扣查至今。據了解，警方今日徵詢律政司意見後，決定起訴當中45人涉嫌暴動等罪行，明日(31日)早上在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n據了解，45人均會被控以暴動罪，部分人會被同時控以阻差辦公、襲擊及藏有攻擊性武器；45人中絕大部分是學生，約三分之一是女性。<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"cfb4b1cb880d8aee830f147d5a64fd2d6ee37550","tid":1386501,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"不分化，各有各做。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba23185cd6bef941ebcb29dcb31eb6edd89120df","tid":1386501,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無野講"}]}